            <h3 class="mt-4">1. Consumer Electronics and Mobile Devices</h3>
            <p>The consumer electronics sector has witnessed substantial GST rate adjustments, particularly benefiting e-commerce platforms that dominate this market segment.</p>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
                    <thead class="thead-dark">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Product Category</th>
