            <p><strong>Impact on E-commerce:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Price Competitiveness:</strong> The 6-10% reduction translates directly to lower prices, making online platforms more attractive</li>
                <li><strong>Increased Demand:</strong> Studies show a 25-30% increase in online electronics sales post-GST reduction</li>
                <li><strong>Improved Margins:</strong> E-commerce platforms can maintain competitive prices while improving profit margins</li>
                <li><strong>Market Expansion:</strong> Lower prices enable penetration into Tier-2 and Tier-3 cities</li>
